        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Protecting Infrastructure and Promoting the Economy Act or the PIPE Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Environmental Protection Agency to establish (1) a wastewater infrastructure discretionary grant program, and (2) a drinking water infrastructure discretionary grant program. Under the programs, state, local, and tribal governments, public water utilities (e.g., systems used to treat wastewater or sewage), and certain water systems may apply for grants for infrastructure projects.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
